Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:11:16.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)}Note: there's really bad audio lag for the first entire half of this stream.\NNot much I can do about it, sorry :/
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:58.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk "This story continues with hope" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Was that alright? I think I bumped the mic a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry for waving my hands all around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kon-more!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This is Mayu Yoshioka, voice of Haruka Kiritani from MMJ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:16.90,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In this edition of ProSeka Aftertalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:24.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we'll look back at this event while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:28.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll be covering the "This story continues with hope" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:34.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Have you been enjoying the event and the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:40.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've personally been really looking forward to this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:46.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Today, especially, since I get to hear everyone's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:52.18,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We've gathered your comments for this Aftertalk sent through email as well as the submissions channel on the Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:55.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone who mailed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:58.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We'd like to go over some of them in our program today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:03.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We got so many, but unfortunately due to time we're only going to be able to cover a few,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but we do appreciate each and every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Also, if you have any thoughts on today's program,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:12.69,Haruka,,0,0,0,,please post them on X with #ProSekaAftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'll also check the Aftertalk hashtag after the program today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,so please make sure to post there as well. We'd appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:31.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright then, I'll be sure to keep up with the YouTube chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but we've got a lot to get through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I also came with a lot to talk about, but—
Comment: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Surprised sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:42.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I brought my notebook for today, but I forgot it in the green room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll ask one of the makeup artists to help me get it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:53.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll start off by talking about the "This story continues with hope" event story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:57.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,How did you feel about the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:04.42,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Let's revisit the highlights of this story together while going over some of the messages you’ve sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:10.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,First up, from "Mirin"-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message, Mirin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Yoshioka-san, 'kon-more'". Kon-more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:19.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I loved your firm yet clear voice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:20.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:27.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I feel like this event showed a lot more of the deliberation than usual."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:32.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This time, MMJ were working together with the other idol groups like Cheer Day towards the same goal."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"And by working together—"
Comment: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,More surprised sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They brought my notebook over for me. We'll go over this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupting your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:48.44,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This time, MMJ were working together with the other idol groups like Cheer Day towards the same goal."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:54.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"It was really cool to watch everyone talk things through, exchange ideas, and go back and forth on different approaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:58.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"and through it all, Haruka-chan taking charge to get things done."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:01.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This was another great chance to see Haruka taking the initiative."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:05.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"It was fun to see her work together with all the other idols."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.89,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Do your best at the LumiGra finals, MMJ!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the abbreviation, "LumiGra".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Shortened from "Lumina Grand Prix."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:21.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think that's the first time I've seen it shortened like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.24,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Have I seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Either way, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Appreciate you writing in, Mirin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:36.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's right, we are at a really important point in the story. This is the stage right before the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:40.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This is the stage where we finally get to see everyone's votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:46.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I know everyone had big expectations for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, I did see lots of people saying "oh boy here it comes..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I feel like they're in great shape to tackle whatever comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I want Haruka as my boss."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"First time seeing 'LumiGra—'" oh, interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's how some are saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:12.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually yeah, that does sound like what people might call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,LumiGra sounds right. Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:29.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, we have one more message to go over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:33.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,From "Yukki"-san, thank you. That's "Yukki" in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kon-more, Yoshioka-san!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Kon-more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:41.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I felt like this story represented a culmination of MMJ's recent efforts."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Seeing the formerly competing idol groups join forces,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"not just to impress the viewers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:52.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"but prioritizing bringing hope to their audience, was really moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:58.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"On top of that, we saw Haruka confronting some of her past trauma as a way of getting through their challenges."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I thought that was extremely cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:04.25,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"And at the end, they were able to get 2nd overall in qualifiers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"and I was yet again moved."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:09.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Yoshioka-san, I'm looking forward to all the ways you'll continue to portray Haruka-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:15.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely. I was so relieved they managed to get 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:19.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But waiting for that announcement was really nerve-wracking, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hearing everyone else get announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:27.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, isn't them announcing the number of votes before the group super realistic too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:32.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Isn't it kind of interesting how everyone gets two votes for this event?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:37.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,You don't just have to choose one, you can go "these guys" and "these guys".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:41.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's a very forgiving system, and seeing the number of comments too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:49.44,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it really allowed them to see exactly how much attention they were actually getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Makes for a pretty interesting event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:17:02.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In real life, you don't really see too many of these kind of nation-wide idol competitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:09.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,so I found myself thinking "what would this look like if it happened in real life?" a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:14.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I voted for MMJ and ReLight! (jk)"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, who would I vote for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:23.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, there were a few units mentioned that didn't directly show up in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:29.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I liked wondering what those groups might have been like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:33.90,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think someone mentioned, you can't use both your votes on the same unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Think it was mentioned somewhere in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:43.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! "The moment 4th place was announced, someone knew they were going home."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:48.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hearing that not everyone in their group was making it through must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I get that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:54.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That other unit "Aimu" did end up passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Getting 2nd is huge win for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:11.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Before the event, Haruka talked about how MMJ should expect a certain position,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,based on the current online rankings. Back during the first episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:19.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I totally get that, trying to get a feel out how the final rankings might end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:23.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,MMJ were definitely checking out all the rankings and predictions on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:33.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All of that might have an influence on their production direction after this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:37.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Proactively seeking out all that information online, and then deciding on a strategy from there;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,isn't that really mature of them? Especially since they're high schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:45.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,How the heck can high schoolers do all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:49.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your message, Yukki-san, and thanks everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:53.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We only got to read these 3 messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:58.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I have so much I want to talk about too, so I'm going to take over a bit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:02.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:05.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The Lumina Grand Prix,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:12.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,for all you ProSeka users, it must definitely feel like it's been going on for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After all, the story is shown just bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:19.62,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I totally get people saying "When are we gonna get to the finals?" or "I wanna see what happens next!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:24.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But actually, I kind of want to just stay right here in this little gap right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:27.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,after all the hard work in the qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:31.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,right between passing the qualifiers and before the finals start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even I was really nervous about the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So when I heard this would be a Haruka focus event, I was like "uehhh,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:42.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I'm covering {\i1}this{\i0} part of the story from Haruka's perspective?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And especially for Haruka,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.01,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we'll go more in depth later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:52.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but it's very obvious that there's a big wall between Haruka and Hiiragi-san, ReLight's producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Something Haruka can't really ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:58.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And the fact that she has to come face to face with him once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Last time she...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,fought with him? Not quite "fought", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:10.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Last time she confronted him face to face,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:17.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it almost felt like this standoff between grown-ups in the corporate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:21.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After which, Haruka had this really down look,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,like "I don't know how we're going to get through this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I think she grew from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:29.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And so when she went to face Hiiragi-san again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:34.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what exactly the confrontation might look like this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:37.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But now that they're working with ReLight in the stage right before finals as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,companions? As a team?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:46.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad she got such reassuring advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:51.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That feeling of security and strength she must get knowing Hiiragi-san has their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Knowing he's this big, influential figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She must feel so relieved knowing "ah, Hiiragi-san has our backs."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:01.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,You could feel that coming from each and every word that he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:06.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think Haruka does truly have respect and admiration for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:13.50,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but at the same time, she knows that someday, she'll have to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That acknowledgement, I feel, was more or less the focus of Episode 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:23.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,He's scary, that Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:29.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's like, the more you rely on him, the more he feels like he's going to be a threat later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:43.69,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So it makes me think, what kind of team was ASRUN back when Hiiragi-san and Haruka were working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So Haruka's main battle was with Hiiragi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:51.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but that's wrapped in the wider context of preparing for the event for the cram school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And all the other teams going to their own various locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:04.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Arisawa-san's... perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,As a former idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:11.15,Haruka,,0,0,0,,her perspective on "this is what I wish I could have done for them".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:15.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even if she's retired, she sees the idols of today and thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:20.48,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I want ensure this generation has that strength to deliver hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ensuring the idols of this world have that... "allure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:28.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:33.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean come on, having that kind of expectation from this legendary idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:36.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,you guys sure have your work cut out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"The story got me really fired up."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:50.37,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah that one was good—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:53.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Kiritani really is dangerous, getting me fired up like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:55.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really like that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:59.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For event recordings, we usually only get to see the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:06.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We don't usually record together, so I only get to see the full conversations in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:12.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But even just looking at the script, I knew that scene with Hiiragi-san and Arisawa-san was going to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:15.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,that was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:22.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was actually going through the story mostly to get to that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:25.37,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, I did want to see the rest of MMJ's scenes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:29.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But that scene was specifically one I wanted to burn into my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:35.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah. Looks like the audio's a bit out of sync so we're going to pause the stream momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:38.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please standby while we fix the issue.
Comment: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:33.57,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--We're back--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.57,0:24:40.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright then, we've been talking a lot about Chapter 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:43.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but let's talk about what happens in the other chapters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like the excursion live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:52.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Two whole weeks for that— if you think about the fact that the whole Lumina Grand Prix leading up to this was less than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:55.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,isn't that pretty crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.49,0:25:00.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They've all had to shuffle teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.51,0:25:03.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and then learn each others' songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.07,0:25:07.18,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and if you think about the fact that they could do that in just a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.18,0:25:11.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,you can tell everyone's gotta have a really young memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:16.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how fast these practice parts go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:20.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially with how fast they must have to learn new songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.53,0:25:26.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Minori's mentioned that she's good at imitating choreo,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.64,0:25:32.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but for other members who aren't so good at that having to learn so quickly—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:35.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,not just the choreo, but the singing parts, the rest of the formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:39.69,Haruka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and{\i0} bringing their own originality while keeping respect for the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.69,0:25:41.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Isn't that way too much to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.97,0:25:43.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Aren't they just so talented?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.65,0:25:45.86,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I need to start learning from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.27,0:25:49.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They're super impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.01,0:25:55.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's one thing I saw that I couldn't stop laughing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:26:07.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The comments. For all the recent MMJ events, you sometimes see the stream viewers' comments pop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:10.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you all aren't the ones writing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.51,0:26:13.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually I think I've seen them before,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.96,0:26:17.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I feel like there's actually a writer specifically for those comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.60,0:26:21.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"They're always really accurate."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.52,0:26:25.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,People are probably like "wait, did they steal that from my tweet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.72,0:26:32.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"You got me." Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:35.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, are they just taking those comments from online,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:38.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,or are they recruiting the actual commenters?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.91,0:26:41.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I always find it super funny to think about how accurate they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.87,0:26:48.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hmm, but I think that's just one part of how realistic these stories have been feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:55.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,In each story, I always like thinking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.52,0:26:59.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"which comments are the ones I'm most likely to have said?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.69,0:27:09.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, there are also times where those comments are actually spoken in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.60,0:27:13.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Any time the fans themselves show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:18.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, for some of the lines from MMJ fans or Cheerful{\fnNoto Serif JP}＊{\fn}Days fans, you'd think;
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.56,0:27:21.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Ahh, I'd definitely say something like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.99,0:27:30.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, and you know, I'm glad we don't hear this as much nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.68,0:27:33.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we don't see it as much, but earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.68,0:27:36.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,there were lots of comments like "MMJ? Who?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.61,0:27:39.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially for Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:44.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,people saying things like "I've been following the other members, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:49.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,there were... there were some pretty tough comments out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.22,0:27:53.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But if you compare it to now, don't you think they've come so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:55.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All the comments are like "Go MMJ!"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.92,0:27:57.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.87,0:28:06.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"The comments are so much nicer now."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.53,0:28:08.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not only nicer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.93,0:28:15.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,they must be so glad that they're really well known now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:18.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like they've even been featured on TV now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.12,0:28:24.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Comments do have real power, don't they?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.44,0:28:31.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"It's their hard work". 100%, it's MMJ's hard work paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.79,0:28:40.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Everyone feels super welcomed by the comments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.96,0:28:43.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They're not worried reading them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.89,0:28:49.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.03,0:28:52.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I feel like if MMJ was to solo stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.97,0:28:57.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,the comment section would have a pretty different vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.52,0:29:01.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, there were fans who have been with them all the way since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.63,0:29:03.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and I feel that part wouldn't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.92,0:29:06.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I bet there'd be lots of comments like "Hey, I'm new here!" Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.49,0:29:09.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I just came from learning about MMJ at the Lumina Grand Prix!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.96,0:29:12.52,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.52,0:29:16.01,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I'm originally a Cheerful{\fnNoto Serif JP}＊{\fn}Days fan, but got interested in MMJ, so I joined their stream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.01,0:29:17.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Something like that hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.85,0:29:24.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Hahaha "Newbies! Welcome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:29.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Everyone'd be like "Welcome!" "Welcome!" Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.01,0:29:34.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Oh, you're a first-timer?" Yeah I could see people saying that haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.05,0:29:43.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Welcome all first-timers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.71,0:29:46.59,Haruka,,0,0,0,,All the veterans might say that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.59,0:29:51.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. "I came from watching the LumiGra."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.17,0:29:55.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Wait, what if LumiGra actually becomes the term official staff use?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.17,0:29:57.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. It's just me calling it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.47,0:30:00.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.87,0:30:04.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That was a bit of a recap on the story as a whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.94,0:30:06.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.67,0:30:08.51,Haruka,,0,0,0,,let's set aside the Chapter 8 discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.51,0:30:11.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,There's actually a specific scene I wanted to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.26,0:30:14.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've chosen a scene I wanted to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.33,0:30:16.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,As you might expect, it's from Chapter 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.87,0:30:18.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:23.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was thinking Chapter 8 too,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.17,0:30:25.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I would start crying if we watched that.
Comment: 0,0:30:25.13,0:30:28.13,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--END PRE-STORY TALK --
Comment: 0,0:38:18.01,0:38:18.01,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN POST STORY TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.01,0:38:23.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, that was Chapter 6 of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.26,0:38:31.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mentioned it a little before we watched, but that conversation between Haruka and Hiiragi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.23,0:38:38.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought the bravery Haruka showed to directly confront him one-on-one was absolutely incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.11,0:38:44.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Knowing that they already faced off during Haruka’s previous focus event, but even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.60,0:38:47.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,still going to meet him again like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.20,0:38:50.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it shows that she has a very different mindset now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.14,0:38:53.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought that was really cool of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.36,0:38:58.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For that confrontation scene, we actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.12,0:38:59.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,we actually did two takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.72,0:39:01.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think they ended up using the second take.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:04.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After going through the first take—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.19,0:39:08.64,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean, for Haruka to go up to Hiiragi-san, this really distinguished producer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.64,0:39:13.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,she would definitely have {\i1}some {\i0}nerves. Maybe feeling like "I don't know what to do next".
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.47,0:39:18.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So I talked with more of a wavering, unsure tone, like she was kind of just casually going to ask for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.88,0:39:21.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But they said, "no, this is—"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.58,0:39:25.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Let Haruka fight for this."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.35,0:39:26.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"With Hiiragi-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.58,0:39:30.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Like, "To get that advice out of him, you need to go in there and {\i1}hunt{\i0} for it."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.77,0:39:33.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But that means you really need to approach him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.08,0:39:40.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Fight him on this; say that we need to cooperate in order to ensure we pass."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.03,0:39:41.01,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I got that direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.01,0:39:44.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and I was like "wow, sounds fun, let's try it."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.55,0:39:47.55,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And so that's how the second take turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.72,0:39:53.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, I feel that one focal point of this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.28,0:39:59.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,is Haruka taking these small steps forward on her journey as a producer herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.35,0:40:05.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really hope that came through clearly in this scene with Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.60,0:40:07.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.71,0:40:10.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The sound producers and directors have all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.61,0:40:14.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,little by little building this character of Haruka alongside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:20.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So hearing them say more things like, "Maybe it's time for Haruka to show a bit of her strength here," makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:26.32,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That particularly comes through in this Chapter 6, so I really wanted to watch it with everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.32,0:40:28.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.23,0:40:30.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:33.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my earring fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.74,0:40:40.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.23,0:40:44.75,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Right, so we'll leave the Chapter 6 discussion at that, and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:46.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,time for the card art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.80,0:40:52.03,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.03,0:40:54.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,We're gonna talk about Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.40,0:40:56.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Chapter 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.20,0:40:58.40,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.40,0:41:02.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,first and foremost, congrats on passing, MMJ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.80,0:41:04.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Big congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:08.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I thought that just making finals would be great,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.94,0:41:11.94,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but to get second place? Aren't they so amazing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.34,0:41:15.93,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So 1st place was Cheerful{\fnNoto Serif JP}＊{\fn}Days,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.93,0:41:17.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and MMJ got 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.17,0:41:24.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,After 3rd and 4th were announced and there were only 2 teams left, hearing Haruka not wanting to give up—
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.81,0:41:27.88,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.88,0:41:29.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She was so cool in that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:33.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even as the other members were losing hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.17,0:41:35.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,she was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.20,0:41:39.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,ah, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.04,0:41:40.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But yeah, that was just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.53,0:41:42.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Seeing her say "We can't give up" like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.05,0:41:46.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And then her being the first to go up and say "Thank you" as their representative....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.04,0:41:50.22,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That "Thank you" honestly made me burst into tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.22,0:41:52.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is all Haruka. I’m just speaking as her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.66,0:41:55.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but man, everything about this scene just makes me just so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.63,0:41:57.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.65,0:42:02.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For that "Thank you"... let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.38,0:42:05.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think we ended up doing two takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.26,0:42:09.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,For the first one, I felt like I had to stay composed and speak very straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.49,0:42:12.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But they said, "Maybe it's okay let a little more emotion out."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.30,0:42:14.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"This is a big moment in the story after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.02,0:42:15.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I thought "You're so right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.63,0:42:18.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So I went for it again, and it came out amazingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:22.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I was like "I'm crying again even the second time around?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.34,0:42:25.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It really was a "thank you" from the bottom of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.87,0:42:29.62,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, Hikarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.62,0:42:32.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She got a respectable 5th place,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.05,0:42:34.92,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but only the top 4 moved on from the qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.92,0:42:40.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,so unfortunately that means this is the end of Hikarin's dream, at least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.84,0:42:45.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But she said she believes that everyone will continue to shine their best in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.73,0:42:50.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think Hikarin's unique style really helped everyone in this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.39,0:42:52.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.31,0:42:57.39,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Seeing her leave even after building that bond with everyone is definitely sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.39,0:43:01.01,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but seeing everyone's hopes and dreams come together,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.01,0:43:08.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,that really made this stand out as a "team" effort for this final qualifier round.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.48,0:43:18.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Also, on a personal note, I was so happy when Hikarin’s character visual was finally added!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.85,0:43:21.57,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I've always been super curious about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.57,0:43:24.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I had an idea just based on her voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.08,0:43:26.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but finally seeing her, she's just super cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.77,0:43:29.05,Haruka,,0,0,0,,There's just so much going on in her design.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.05,0:43:33.90,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted to learn more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.90,0:43:36.45,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"I hope they get to perform together again one day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.45,0:43:40.31,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I’m also curious about what kind of songs Hikarin actually sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.14,0:43:43.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.84,0:43:48.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So, we'll move on to card art discussion in a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.11,0:43:51.11,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and in Airi's? Yeah, in Airi's card, Hikarin shows up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.11,0:43:58.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it. When you build up a "persona" too much, it gets really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.86,0:44:02.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Keeping up a persona is definitely a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.27,0:44:07.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely get over it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.07,0:44:11.98,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But it's because she overcame that struggle that we can see Hikarin as she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.98,0:44:13.47,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm really rooting for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.47,0:44:17.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And as for what lies ahead in the finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.96,0:44:21.82,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it's finally coming. Remember, this has all just been the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.82,0:44:25.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's only gonna get tougher from here. Just four teams left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.12,0:44:30.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm excited to see exactly what's in store for them going forward.
Comment: 0,0:44:31.81,0:44:37.55,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN CARD TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.81,0:44:34.42,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that, let's move on to the event cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.90,0:44:39.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, to start us off...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:44.53,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Haruka-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.68,0:44:48.17,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.17,0:44:51.17,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}This was super cool, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.17,0:44:54.37,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}When her banner event was announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.37,0:44:57.12,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I felt like I needed to fix my posture\Nand stand up straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.12,0:45:02.35,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I remember grinning to myself, like "nah, she'd win."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.35,0:45:03.55,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.55,0:45:04.63,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I was like "Hiii!"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.63,0:45:06.22,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Thank you for the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.22,0:45:06.75,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Yeah, guys, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.75,0:45:07.53,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.34,0:45:16.88,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Look at the—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.88,0:45:20.91,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh, you can't see what I'm pointing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.91,0:45:24.07,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These gloves. They're the kind that aren't— full?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.07,0:45:26.25,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}They don't come down all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.25,0:45:27.77,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}What do you call those?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.77,0:45:29.01,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I mean, these were like—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.01,0:45:31.84,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These look amazing on our Haruka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.84,0:45:34.43,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.43,0:45:38.08,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Gotta remember to talk about the whole costume\Nafter these little detailed parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.08,0:45:41.08,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And those sparkles are also so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.01,0:45:47.33,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Gotta keep moving on. Else we'll be here all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.33,0:45:48.57,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.57,0:45:51.26,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Yeah, this is the one I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.26,0:45:53.53,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hikarin and Airi in the cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.53,0:45:56.04,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}These two were also really cute~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.04,0:45:58.57,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Kind of looks like they're part of a talk show.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.57,0:46:01.88,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Definitely looks like they're\Nready to liven the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.88,0:46:07.92,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So cute. Actually, when I first saw her character sprite, Hikarin was a bit shorter than I was expecting,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.92,0:46:09.12,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}but I think that makes her cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.44,0:46:15.76,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Airi's also really good here, isn't she? And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.76,0:46:18.40,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So pretty here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.40,0:46:20.35,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.35,0:46:22.48,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh, try rotating her straight up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.48,0:46:24.51,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Think it looks really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.62,0:46:31.20,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Lighting is so pretty, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.20,0:46:34.03,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And the illumination from the back, like—
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.03,0:46:37.20,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(650,750)}Kasaaa{\i0}. So good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.31,0:46:39.84,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.84,0:46:41.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Right, gotta keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.38,0:46:44.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Otherwise you'll only get a view of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.97,0:46:48.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, Len-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.56,0:46:53.26,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}This was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.21,0:46:57.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh look, there’s a little penguin on her notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.65,0:46:58.83,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.83,0:47:00.94,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}We know Haruka loves her penguins.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.94,0:47:02.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She even has one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.46,0:47:08.91,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Wait a sec, I think she even has a penguin thing\N on her pencil case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.91,0:47:12.13,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Actually, I think Len's sprite has...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.13,0:47:14.83,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}his old costume? Can you call it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.83,0:47:17.07,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}The one he started with.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:21.36,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}But seeing his new outfit in a card art like this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.49,0:47:24.62,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And here's cool Len.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.15,0:47:29.98,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Beautiful. Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.98,0:47:33.09,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}It's too much, I can't even look at him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.09,0:47:34.60,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Hiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.60,0:47:36.21,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.21,0:47:38.26,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah this was also so good—
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.26,0:47:41.76,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}wait a sec, is this really only a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.76,0:47:43.20,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Just a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.20,0:47:47.38,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, so cute, so pretty, just as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.38,0:47:50.53,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}She's so dazzling. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.53,0:47:54.31,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And the trained. Are you sure this is a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.13,0:47:57.37,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Is this really a 3-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.37,0:47:59.16,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I don't even know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.16,0:48:01.97,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And finally Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.97,0:48:03.48,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.48,0:48:08.10,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}So for this set, the card arts have this night sky theming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.10,0:48:09.76,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}They're wearing mostly black,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.76,0:48:13.80,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}and in this card, you can really see the outfit's outline more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.80,0:48:17.26,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}And I'm really glad to see the green under the outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.26,0:48:20.69,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}MMJ's color. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.69,0:48:22.28,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.28,0:48:23.34,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.34,0:48:27.14,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Alright, so that was all the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.14,0:48:32.33,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}We also have a comment about the outfits from the \Ncard illustration production team we'd like to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.33,0:48:37.17,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}"In this story, MMJ had to work together with the other idol groups to face a new challenge in an unfamiliar environment."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.17,0:48:41.52,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}The story revolves around Haruka taking active role\Nfor the sake of her team's success.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.52,0:48:45.12,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Drawing inspiration from the joint live from the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.12,0:48:46.41,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}and laser-focusing on our design,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.41,0:48:50.91,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}we aimed to portray a striking MMJ against a midnight sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.91,0:48:53.65,Haruka - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}To achieve this, we chose a black fabric as the base,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.65,0:48:57.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,adorned with star-shaped accessories for a simple yet eye-catching design.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.70,0:49:02.43,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The design comes together for a "starry night" theme while remaining distinct from those of Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.43,0:49:06.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Since the outfit is composed of 80-90% black fabric,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.76,0:49:13.26,Haruka,,0,0,0,,to avoid looking tacky, we used velvet and satin textures to create a high-end luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.26,0:49:20.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And with lots of detailed accents, we wanted to give MMJ a new, more grown-up impression with these outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.74,0:49:24.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. You know what velvet is?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.16,0:49:27.06,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's what those really nice-feeling carpets are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.06,0:49:29.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The ones that you feel like want to keep touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.70,0:49:33.16,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Using that kind of stuff to make idol outfits is...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.16,0:49:35.87,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Velvet's pretty common in winter-style clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.87,0:49:39.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It works especially well around now like in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.20,0:49:42.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it looks really lustrous and high quality when it catches the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.58,0:49:43.76,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Same with satin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.76,0:49:49.25,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Satin gives off more of a really nice, bright sparkle when the light hits it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.25,0:49:52.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but velvet has this surprising sense of weight and depth to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.14,0:49:56.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It has this really nice way of taking in the light and reflecting it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.58,0:50:01.14,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But wait, isn't it amazing how they're able to portray specific fabrics through just the art?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.14,0:50:02.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.73,0:50:07.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,This right here is where the attention to detail in MMJ outfits really stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.45,0:50:11.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh whoops, we're a bit over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:14.78,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Are we good to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.78,0:50:17.96,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Aaaaahhhh I'm gonna cry~
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.96,0:50:20.67,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's time to watch the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.67,0:50:23.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.09,0:50:26.09,Haruka,,0,0,0,,even if you've just listened to the song, seriously, watch the 3DMV too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.09,0:50:27.18,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.18,0:50:30.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess we're watching it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.02,0:50:36.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So moving on, let's watch the 3DMV created for this event's song thanks to the work of Karasuya Sabou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.19,0:50:38.70,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and then take some time to talk about the song itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.70,0:50:40.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So without further ado, onto the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.71,0:50:41.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Comment: 0,0:44:31.81,0:44:37.55,--DIVIDER--,,0,0,0,,--BEGIN CARD TALK--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.21,0:52:20.16,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.36,0:52:24.15,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That was Polar Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.81,0:52:28.35,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.35,0:52:30.24,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I love everything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.24,0:52:33.81,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Eh, ah, umm, yeah right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.18,0:52:38.82,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right here, their expressions each change one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.82,0:52:42.72,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And this is from the side of the stage, fans normally can't see them from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.72,0:52:45.88,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,But RIGHT HERE THE SHOT FROM BEHIND INTO THAT LOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.88,0:52:48.03,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.03,0:52:49.18,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.18,0:52:53.26,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,This is what everyone's talking about, right? That part right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.26,0:52:54.52,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So that's what you all mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.52,0:52:56.32,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.32,0:52:59.09,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh way too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.09,0:53:04.72,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I mean come on. The quality of the MVs nowadays is just so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.72,0:53:07.58,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right? They've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.58,0:53:08.94,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Look look, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.94,0:53:10.44,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Hold up— right here—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.44,0:53:11.40,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.26,0:53:15.63,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,They look so good in sync like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.63,0:53:16.55,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,yeah this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:21.26,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,THIS PART TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.26,0:53:26.46,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, the night sky scenery, so pretty. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.46,0:53:30.58,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The— ah! Look at the shooting stars! So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.58,0:53:32.43,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And wait for it— this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.43,0:53:33.83,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.83,0:53:35.12,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.12,0:53:36.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And then—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.10,0:53:39.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And then they change formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.10,0:53:39.84,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.84,0:53:42.30,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Now each of them looks up, and— it's the steps—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.30,0:53:44.45,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Then here—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.45,0:53:46.34,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Look, look, it's really subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.34,0:53:48.06,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.06,0:53:49.04,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And then they all—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.04,0:53:50.24,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.24,0:53:53.78,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.78,0:53:56.82,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,This part was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.82,0:54:00.08,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The first time I watched the video, I was like "What's that up there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.15,0:54:06.17,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Back when the 3DMVs were just the on-stage dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.17,0:54:09.73,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,they did a great job of showing what the whole performance might have looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.73,0:54:13.17,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I definitely loved those back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.17,0:54:16.98,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,but the recent ones are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.98,0:54:20.54,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're like whole music videos now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.54,0:54:27.88,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,They're to a point now where they can tell more of a whole story around the song and lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.88,0:54:30.57,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The lighting was incredible in this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.57,0:54:34.08,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,We saw the same thing in the card arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.08,0:54:36.29,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,but the lighting from those stars flying around,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.29,0:54:39.01,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,plus that light shining from behind? The halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.01,0:54:40.06,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,What exactly was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.06,0:54:42.20,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was, it looked amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.20,0:54:45.12,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The whole thing was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.12,0:54:48.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I'm just hopeless.  I could just watch this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.57,0:54:52.96,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Next time you watch this,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.96,0:54:55.63,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,definitely watch out for Airi blowing a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.63,0:54:58.08,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,and Haruka's wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:55:02.13,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Try thinking of them as your oshis.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.13,0:55:03.22,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.22,0:55:07.92,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The MV makes— the outfits look great in the MV as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.92,0:55:11.26,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm done. Watched too many times. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.61,0:55:15.79,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Right, we should move onto talking about the song itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.47,0:55:20.72,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So speaking of "Polar Star",
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.72,0:55:24.47,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Haruka’s events have definitely had a streak of "cool" songs lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.47,0:55:32.13,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So I excited to see what kind of song we'd see this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.13,0:55:37.31,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Looking at the last two songs, I realized that "cool" can come in many varieties,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.31,0:55:40.31,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,so I thought, there's a lot more to explore in the "cool" of idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.31,0:55:44.59,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And so I first saw this song as representing "cool through beauty",
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.59,0:55:47.76,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Its refined coolness felt really fresh,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.76,0:55:51.60,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,and it totally blew me away the first time I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.60,0:55:53.62,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Especially since—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.62,0:55:58.90,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,'Haruka's previous songs have very beautiful harmonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.90,0:56:00.75,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That's one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.75,0:56:05.48,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,But there's also those parts everyone comes in one by one, layering harmonies on top of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.48,0:56:09.55,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,All the small steps MMJ are taking in recent events,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.55,0:56:12.54,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,leading them to success and seeing real results;
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.54,0:56:17.60,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I think those layered harmonies captures all of that really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.60,0:56:21.73,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The harmonies throughout the song are also so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.73,0:56:25.94,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,They layered together so many different vocal lines to create those,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.94,0:56:30.01,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,both in the parts where they sing individually, and going into each chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.01,0:56:34.85,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Try going back and listen closely to all those different vocal layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.85,0:56:39.88,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,As for the recording, what I tried to keep in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.88,0:56:42.29,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,well first of all, was trying not to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.29,0:56:45.39,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Trying to keep composed during those parts—
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.39,0:56:48.14,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,We're idols, so our job is to deliver hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.14,0:56:50.54,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So we ourselves mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.54,0:56:53.48,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,But this is a song reminiscing on all that they've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.48,0:57:00.80,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,as well as reaffirming their drive to keep pushing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.80,0:57:04.68,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So there's a balance being struck between this cool, noble feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.68,0:57:07.83,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,while at the same time portraying an emotional nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.83,0:57:10.48,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That's what makes this song so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.48,0:57:13.81,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That's what I wrote. Here in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.81,0:57:16.94,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Alright, and also,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.94,0:57:20.27,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,there's also going to be a 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.27,0:57:20.96,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.96,0:57:23.86,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So it'll probably also be a full version.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.86,0:57:30.04,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That'll include parts that you don't see here in the 3DMV,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.04,0:57:34.39,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So try listening to both and seeing what's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.39,0:57:40.80,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Specifically, the singing in last chorus might have a bit of a different feel from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.80,0:57:42.52,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So please do try listening to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.52,0:57:45.44,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,With that, actually, on a personal note,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.44,0:57:48.32,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I, Mayu Yoshioka, have actually written lyrics for a song
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.32,0:57:52.58,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,themed around the North Star before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.58,0:57:56.94,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,"Polar Star" meaning the same thing as the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.94,0:58:02.40,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,But "idols" and "stars", especially the North Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.40,0:58:04.92,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,have this natural connection to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.92,0:58:08.15,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,When I was writing those lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.15,0:58:12.90,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I thought of it taking the meaning of a landmark, as a guiding light for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.90,0:58:17.78,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,You know, since the North Star is the brightest in the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.78,0:58:22.12,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,using that to represent a guiding light for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.12,0:58:28.31,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,It represents this feeling of "just watch me" or "find me" really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.31,0:58:29.26,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,That's the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.26,0:58:31.46,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And that—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.46,0:58:37.46,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,For MMJ's story, especially in this Lumina Grand Prix arc,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.46,0:58:41.18,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,that really resonates with finding the image of what an idol should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.18,0:58:46.58,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I thought, "Yeah, that's part of their story". Think I mentioned this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.58,0:58:53.43,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,It's part of an idol's storytelling. That story an idol creates together with their fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.43,0:58:56.46,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,that guiding light is a huge part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.46,0:58:59.00,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The lyricist definitely—
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.00,0:59:00.80,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,you feel the same thing from the lyrics—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.90,0:59:07.79,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.79,0:59:11.95,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Sorry for ranting on about a personal experience like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.95,0:59:13.96,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,but after seeing the title and the lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.96,0:59:20.18,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I felt like "ah, I wasn't alone in those feelings". It was really validating.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.18,0:59:24.04,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I trusted in my feelings back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.04,0:59:30.42,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,My feelings towards idols, the way I think about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.42,0:59:32.19,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,everything that Haruka's taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.19,0:59:34.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,knowing I wasn't wrong in any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.10,0:59:37.50,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,and where MMJ goes from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.50,0:59:43.38,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Being able to reaffirm to myself all my thoughts on what it means to be an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.38,0:59:45.37,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I think this song really helped me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.37,0:59:52.62,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful we had such wonderful lyrics written for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.62,0:59:57.58,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,The "stars" theming has been mostly for Leo/need up to this point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.58,1:00:00.74,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,As far as ProSeka goes, that's kind of been their thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.74,1:00:05.26,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I think the other units have all been kind of avoiding the overlap in theme.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.26,1:00:09.13,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,But now that the characters and stories are pretty well established,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.13,1:00:15.72,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,as a challenge, they mentioned that they wanted MMJ to try taking on a star theme.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.72,1:00:17.87,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.87,1:00:22.62,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Haruka being entrusted to take on a challenge like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.62,1:00:24.63,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,at such an important point in the story,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.63,1:00:27.53,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't be more glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.90,1:00:32.34,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,There was still some more I wanted to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.24,1:00:36.05,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.05,1:00:41.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I think my absolute favorite part of the song was the harmonies,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.10,1:00:42.80,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,and that part going into the ending...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.44,1:00:47.10,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,where the singing changes in the final chorus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.10,1:00:51.33,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,so definitely check out the differences between the 2DMV full version and the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.33,1:00:52.19,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.19,1:00:56.62,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,the 2DMV and 3DMV are now on the official ProSeka YouTube channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.62,1:01:00.36,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,I've been talking so long that they've already been released.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.36,1:01:03.15,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,So please check them out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:07.63,Haruka - Song,,0,0,0,,It's just so good...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.63,1:01:11.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Even all the stage decorations looked really good...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.29,1:01:14.91,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that, that felt only like a short time,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.91,1:01:18.27,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but this ProSeka AfterTalk "This story continues with hope" Edition
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.27,1:01:20.80,Haruka,,0,0,0,,is coming to a close.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.80,1:01:22.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Let's close out by reading some comments.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.96,1:01:32.71,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I feel like I was only saying "so good".
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.67,1:01:39.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we had a chance to all watch the 3DMV together.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.13,1:01:41.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That was really fun,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.30,1:01:44.35,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and also being able to read all your comments in real time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.35,1:01:48.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I really enjoy being able to spend time with you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.94,1:01:53.13,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the otaku speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.13,1:01:56.56,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Probably couldn't make out lots of what I said. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.13,1:01:56.56,Note,,0,0,0,,You're telling me...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.46,1:02:00.97,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"Haruka is so cool."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.97,1:02:03.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Haruka is very cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.10,1:02:05.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,You know, I bet,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.17,1:02:07.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Haruka will get more unbelievably cool from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.58,1:02:09.28,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I believe she will.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.28,1:02:14.65,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Especially now, I think she'll continue to establish herself as a producer.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.65,1:02:19.50,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm not sure why, but after reading the recent MMJ stories,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.50,1:02:21.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm not nervous for them at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.12,1:02:25.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,If anything, I feel excited... more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.95,1:02:27.66,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I don't feel worried at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.66,1:02:30.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,And I think that's because everyone— everyone in MMJ,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.60,1:02:33.60,Haruka,,0,0,0,,is so devoted to their mission to deliver hope,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.60,1:02:39.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,and they just keep pushing forward towards their goals for the sake of their fans.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.02,1:02:40.81,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.81,1:02:45.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,it almost feels nostalgic to remember how nervous I was for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.33,1:02:46.84,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.84,1:02:51.38,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I look at them thinking "I wonder what kind of hope they're going to bring this time."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.38,1:02:54.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I think that's real growth there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.73,1:02:58.12,Haruka,,0,0,0,,MMJ are just so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.12,1:03:00.99,Haruka,,0,0,0,,MMJ are the best!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.10,1:03:03.42,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Right? www
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.47,1:03:11.20,Haruka,,0,0,0,,As you might already know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.20,1:03:14.00,Haruka,,0,0,0,,in the ProSeka livestream the other day,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.00,1:03:18.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,this episode will be the last event Aftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.30,1:03:21.07,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Was it really okay for me to do the last one?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.07,1:03:24.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I mean come on, I was barely speaking coherently.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.63,1:03:26.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,My inner otaku came out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.95,1:03:29.29,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Was it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.29,1:03:30.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.55,1:03:34.83,Haruka,,0,0,0,,just speaking plainly for a second,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.83,1:03:38.19,Haruka,,0,0,0,,going like "that was so good!" or "what about that line?",
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.19,1:03:41.23,Haruka,,0,0,0,,or "that scene was awesome!", or "this art though" with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.23,1:03:44.63,Haruka,,0,0,0,,being able to do that is just so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.63,1:03:46.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,How long have these been going on? 3 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.85,1:03:48.77,Haruka,,0,0,0,,2 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.77,1:03:49.90,Haruka,,0,0,0,,5 years? 4 or 5 years?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.90,1:03:51.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,That long? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.61,1:03:55.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,The Aftertalks have been going on for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.39,1:04:05.10,Haruka,,0,0,0,,It's definitely sad that we're not going to be able to talk about each and every event anymore,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.10,1:04:09.34,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I definitely think there'll be more ways in the future we'll be able to get together.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.34,1:04:12.58,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Personally speaking, I'm absolutely down to do more of these whenever.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.58,1:04:17.30,Haruka,,0,0,0,,As long as there's a place for it, I can definitely keep talking like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.30,1:04:21.33,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Not just for Haruka events, any MMJ focuses too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.33,1:04:23.79,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So even if we don't do this every time anymore,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.79,1:04:30.02,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm personally wishing that we can continue talking maybe to recap at certain milestone points.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.40,1:04:36.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Man, I kind of wish that I could just talk about all the 3DMVs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.74,1:04:38.08,Haruka,,0,0,0,,They're all so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.08,1:04:40.21,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Not even just the Haruka event commissions,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.21,1:04:42.95,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Every one I watch, I'm always like "wow these are so good!"
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.95,1:04:45.49,Haruka,,0,0,0,,"So good!" every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.27,1:04:48.36,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much again, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.78,1:04:54.85,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and so remember to keep watching all the past Aftertalks too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.85,1:04:58.17,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'm probably going to look at today's show and cringe at the otaku speak,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.17,1:05:03.37,Haruka,,0,0,0,,but I'm always ready to talk like this, so let's just hope, and pray that another chance will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.37,1:05:05.72,Haruka,,0,0,0,,I'll also come prepared with lots of notes again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.33,1:05:11.61,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Ah right, we're also putting out more short-form content now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.61,1:05:14.68,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Seems like there's good effort being put in, so please look forward to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.68,1:05:22.46,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So with that, if you still haven't read through the "This story continues with hope" event story, once the next event starts,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.46,1:05:25.74,Haruka,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to read the entire event story.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.74,1:05:30.04,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone here's probably read it. We've mentioned so many spoilers.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.04,1:05:33.41,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Watch it again, then. Go back and watch it with a fresh perspective.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.41,1:05:35.73,Haruka,,0,0,0,,So one more time, thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.73,1:05:37.89,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.89,1:05:39.62,Haruka,,0,0,0,,Bye bye! Thank you!
